              "free_text": [
                " Rubidium-bromide",
                " was used as target, Rubidium and Bromine have atomic",
                " number 37 and 35, respectively, which makes it",
                " impossible to determine the target nucleus of the",
                " spallation reaction"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Pellets fabricated from 99.9%-pure RbBr powder Each",
                "packet typically contained a target and a number of",
                "monitor and recoil-catcher foils. Elemental Al, with",
                "a purity of 99.997% and thickness of 0.025 mm, was",
                "used for the beam monitors and the forward and",
                "backward recoil catchers. RbBr tablets had",
                "thicknesses of 5-6 mm. Foil and RbBr pellet diameters",
                "were approximately 1.3 cm."
              ]
            }
